# intermediate-hot-spot-0.in
4
0-3 o

# Synchronize all threads to start at the exact same time
.

# All 4 threads start a transaction
0 S 100
1 S 101
2 S 102
3 S 103

# All threads read from the highly contested "hot spot" (Address 42)
0 R 42
1 R 42
2 R 42
3 R 42

# All threads try to write to the hot spot
0 W 42 10
1 W 42 20
2 W 42 30
3 W 42 40

# All threads attempt to commit simultaneously
# 3 of these should naturally abort and retry under the hood
0 C 100
1 C 101
2 C 102
3 C 103

# Wait for everyone to finish
.
0-3 x